WEBVTT

22:53.870 --> 22:55.070 line:80%
Cornel water.

22:55.590 --> 22:57.390 line:80%
I got a bigger bottle this time.

22:57.440 --> 22:58.960 line:80%
Last time it ran out at a critical moment.

22:58.960 --> 23:00.220 line:80%
This should be enough.

23:00.280 --> 23:01.810 line:80%
If sprayed in the eyes, it causes
swelling, pain,

23:01.810 --> 23:03.810 line:80%
and temporary blindness for 3 days.
